@startuml
title 结算中心流程（T+1/T+7/T+30 结算周期）

skinparam participant {
  BackgroundColor #FEFEFE
  BorderColor #555555
}

!define SERVICE_COLOR #E8F5E9
!define ENGINE_COLOR #E3F2FD
!define DB_COLOR #F3E5F5
!define MQ_COLOR #FFF3E0
!define EXT_COLOR #FFEBEE

actor "财务运营" as finance #FFECB3
participant "settlement-service\n(结算中心)" as ss #ENGINE_COLOR
participant "payment-core\n(支付核心)" as pc #SERVICE_COLOR
database "OceanBase\n(结算单)" as ob #DB_COLOR
queue "RocketMQ" as mq #MQ_COLOR
participant "accounting-service\n(会计引擎)" as acct #SERVICE_COLOR
participant "merchant-bank\n(银行/出款)" as bank #EXT_COLOR
participant "notification\n(通知服务)" as notif #SERVICE_COLOR

== 结算周期触发 ==

ss -> ss: Cron 触发结算\n(结算截止日 23:59:59)
note right #E3F2FD
  结算周期类型:
  - T+1 每日结算
  - T+7 每周结算
  - T+30 每月结算
  由 Apollo 配置 merchant.settle.cycle
end note

== Step 1: 生成结算单 ==

ss -> pc: queryOrderByPeriod(merchantId, period)
activate pc
pc --> ss: 返回期间内已支付/已退款订单列表
deactivate pc

ss -> ss: 汇总计算:
note right
  - 有效交易总额（已支付 - 已退款）
  - 平台佣金（按商户费率表）
  - 通道手续费（按渠道费率）
  - 退款预扣（期间内已发起退款）
  - 净额 = 交易总额 - 佣金 - 手续费 - 退款
end note

ss -> ob: INSERT settlement_order
activate ob
ob --> ss: settlement_no = SET20260613001
deactivate ob

ss -> ob: INSERT settlement_bill (逐单明细)
activate ob
ob --> ss: 批量写入成功
deactivate ob

== Step 2: 结算审核 ==

alt 自动审核（额度 < ¥500,000）
    ss -> ss: autoApprove()
    ss -> ob: UPDATE status = APPROVED
else 人工审核（额度 ≥ ¥500,000）
    ss -> finance: 待审核结算单通知
    activate finance
    finance -> ss: 审核通过 / 驳回
    deactivate finance
    ss -> ob: UPDATE status = APPROVED / REJECTED
end

== Step 3: 出款执行 ==

alt 余额充足
    ss -> bank: payout(merchantAccount, netAmount)
    activate bank
    note right #FFEBEE
      银行代付接口
      支持对公/对私账户
    end note
    bank --> ss: payout_success(tradeNo)
    deactivate bank
    ss -> ob: UPDATE status = TRANSFERRED
    activate ob
    ob --> ss: 更新完成
    deactivate ob
else 余额不足
    ss -> ss: 标记 WAITING_FUNDS
    ss -> finance: P2 告警: 结算账户余额不足
    note right #FFCDD2
      等待财务运营充值后
      手动触发出款
    end note
end

== Step 4: 账务处理 ==

ss -> mq: publish SettlementCompletedEvent
activate mq
mq --> ss: publish ok
deactivate mq

mq -> acct: 消费 SettlementCompletedEvent
activate acct
acct -> ob: INSERT account_journal
note right #E3F2FD
  借: 应收账款  ¥10,000
  贷: 主营业务收入 ¥9,600
  贷: 应付手续费  ¥300
  贷: 应交税费    ¥100
end note
acct --> mq: 记账完成
deactivate acct

== Step 5: 商家通知 ==

mq -> notif: 消费 SettlementCompletedEvent
activate notif
notif -> notif: 生成结算报告
notif --> mq: 通知已发送
deactivate notif

note right #FEFEFE
  通知渠道:
  - 商家工作台消息
  - 邮件发送结算报告
  - 短信提醒 (大额)
end note

== Step 6: 退款预扣（跨周期场景） ==

note over ss #FFF3E0
  场景: 本期已结算的订单
  在下一周期发生退款
  处理: 从下一期结算净额中抵扣
end note

ss -> ss: 查询本期退款预扣明细
ss -> ob: UPDATE settlement_order.adjustment
ss -> ob: 生成负向结算单 (退款冲抵)

@enduml
